1
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,959
Mr. Zhao, do you need something?

2
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,280
Zhao Qihai, what are you doing?

3
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,400
Let go of me.

4
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,640
Do you...

5
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,000
know something?

6
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,680
Know what?

7
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:16,640
I'm asking you one last time.

8
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,640
Zhao Qihai.

9
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:21,239
The dirty things you did,

10
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,519
can't be hidden anymore.

11
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,480
Even if I know, so what?

12
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,959
As long as Zhao Qishan doesn't know, it's fine.

13
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:40,079
Besides, they are already dead.

14
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,120
Di Fu is dead too.

15
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,120
What are you still afraid of?

16
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,000
You're afraid I'll tell?

17
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,640
Even if I tell, so what?

18
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,079
No one cares.

19
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,039
Thirty seconds.

20
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,759
Do you even last that long?

21
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:19,120
Say that again.

22
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,800
I know.

23
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,680
You're afraid others will know you can't perform.

24
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,599
Stinking witch.

25
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,680
You dare hit me?

26
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,479
Jerk.

27
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,199
You can't perform.

28
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,759
Shut up.

29
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,000
Kill me if you have the guts.

30
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:56,000
Save me from living in torment every day.

31
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,639
What are you tormented about?

32
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,879
Zhao Qihai.

33
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,439
My unbearable past,

34
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,400
who is it actually because of?

35
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,639
Do you really think I'm stupid?

36
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,879
I suffered abuse and humiliation,

37
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,039
and now you want me to be grateful

38
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,039
to the mastermind?

39
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,840
Is this fair?

40
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,280
Is it fair?

41
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:09,240
Brother-in-law's last words said

42
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:12,039
he willingly let my sister kill him.

43
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,560
He is already dead.

44
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,240
Why keep stabbing him?

45
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,439
Miss Asi.

46
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,639
You two.

47
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,480
When the master was alive, this study

48
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,319
was off-limits to outsiders.

49
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,199
We're leaving right away.

50
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:30,959
By the way,

51
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,240
Miss Asi.

52
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:34,040
There's something I want to ask you.

53
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,600
This is the primary crime scene,

54
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,720
but it feels very new here.

55
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,240
Someone cleaned it.

56
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:42,839
Yes.

57
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,120
It was with the police's consent.

58
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,240
The day after the police withdrew,

59
00:04:48,759 --> 00:04:50,639
I had someone clean this place up.

60
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:54,879
Then we're leaving.

61
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,160
Actually,

62
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,040
the power is back.

63
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:19,040
It's ten minutes to midnight.

64
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,439
What did you want to say just now?

65
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,079
Nothing.

66
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,319
I'm hungry.

67
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,680
If you're not sleepy,

68
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,920
come with me to the dining room for some food.

69
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,839
The Tower of Babel.

70
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:36,920
It was created by the painter Bruegel in 1563

71
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:40,439
based on a story from the Bible.

72
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,000
Story.

73
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,560
Its story,

74
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:49,000
tells of human ancestors trying to escape the flood,

75
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,560
on the only land available,

76
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,480
building such a tower to reach the sky.

77
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,519
And thus angered God.

78
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:58,439
Maybe humans wanted to try using this tower

79
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,000
to reach heaven,

80
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,519
challenging His authority.

81
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,439
But since it's a famous painting,

82
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,879
how could it be placed here so casually?

83
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,879
This is a replica for decoration.

84
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,279
The original is in the Art History Museum in Vienna.

85
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,279
Inspector Qi,

86
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,199
I didn't expect you to know this.

87
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,000
How would I know?

88
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,920
I saw it in my son's extracurricular books.

89
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,639
Then this Zhao Qishan,

90
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,600
did he want to become God?

91
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,600
What do you mean?

92
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:30,920
Because the name of this villa is the Tower of Babel.

93
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:42,920
This

94
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,800
is the recording of everyone's stories today.

95
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,639
But I still feel they are lying.

96
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,920
Perhaps from their words,

97
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,279
we can find some hidden motives.

98
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:59,319
Only people hiding secrets will lie.

99
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:01,439
And these secrets themselves

100
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:02,360
are

101
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,639
the key to solving the mystery.

102
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,240
Maybe the truth will come out tomorrow.

103
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,519
I'm full. Going to sleep.

104
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,879
Inspector Qi, you...

105
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,439
You could scare someone to death like that, you know?

106
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,319
If you haven't done anything wrong,

107
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,120
what are you afraid of?

108
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,439
Still up this late?

109
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,839
I'm discussing cooperation with Boss Tan.

110
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,879
My brother died.

111
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:10,560
I have a duty to finish his unfinished business.

112
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,720
Is that a problem?

113
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:12,800
No problem.

114
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:15,360
Good night.

115
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:26,079
Botticelli's famous painting,

116
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:27,399
*Dante's Inferno*,

117
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:31,240
is the Western world's depiction of hell.

118
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,320
I haven't been in this room before.

119
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,960
Only back at the police station,

120
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,240
I saw photos of the scene.

121
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,440
I overlooked this painting.

122
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,440
Yesterday I talked to Miss Li about the *Tower of Babel* painting.

123
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,879
I've been thinking,

124
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,679
whether these two paintings

125
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,639
have any connection.

126
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,679
These two paintings,

127
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:53,840
seem to be inverted versions of each other.

128
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,519
Heaven is Hell.

129
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:59,080
Hell is the mortal world.

130
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:01,759
And then?

131
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,039
That's it.

132
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:08,000
I haven't figured it out yet.

133
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,120
But maybe I will...

134
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:11,480
Miss Li.

135
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:12,240
Li Ran.

136
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,200
Inspector Qi.

137
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:18,559
My sister and brother-in-law just passed away.

138
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,600
I don't have the time or the mood

139
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,399
to joke with you.

140
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,720
I was just wondering,

141
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,240
what is the connection between these two paintings.

142
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:32,679
Zhao Qishan put these two paintings in the villa.

143
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,279
*Dante's Inferno* hangs above.

144
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,080
*Tower of Babel* is placed below.

145
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,799
*Tower of Babel* hangs in the dining room,

146
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,240
where everyone coming and going can see it.

147
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,039
Do you think this implies that

148
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,440
Heaven is right before our eyes?

149
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,600
This...

150
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,279
This is my daughter's necklace.

151
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,039
This is my daughter's.

152
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,039
A gold Buddha necklace.

153
00:10:05,879 --> 00:10:07,240
An emerald ring.

154
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:14,679
I gave it to her after she became a streamer.

155
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,639
I gave this to her.

156
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,639
She always wore it.

157
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,720
After I woke up,

158
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,399
it was right by the pillow.

159
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,320
Right there.

160
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,559
My daughter always wore it.

161
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:34,679
Mr. Fang.

162
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,919
My daughter always wore it.

163
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,360
Is the thing on your neck gone?

164
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,080
My daughter always wore it.

165
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,320
My daughter always wore it.

166
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:45,480
I don't have anything on my neck.

167
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,440
Mr. Fang.

168
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,279
When you came in yesterday,

169
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:52,240
I noticed you were indeed wearing a necklace.

170
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:53,440
Is it this one?

171
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:58,840
No.

172
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,440
You're lying!

173
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,320
Give me back my daughter!

174
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,039
Give me back my daughter!
